title: Cheugy, or Not Cheugy, That is the Questrend 5/13: CDC, John Mulaney, Hip Hop Debuts, RATM
itunes:title: Cheugy, or Not Cheugy, That is the Questrend 5/13: CDC, John Mulaney, Hip Hop Debuts, RATM
description:
On this edition of Cheugy, or Not Cheugy, That is the Questrend Jack and Miles discuss the CDC lifting their mask, John Mulaney getting divorced and hooking up with Olivia Munn in one fell swoop, the best debut hip hop albums, and RATM's surprisingly leftist politics.
